me":"2020-09-08T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"sony出左幾個錢呀，我叫富士比多幾蚊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03c10bd08a5c9599ccc7cf3aec6da86e55fbadc","tid":2193774,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"好似4/3有d都大過full frame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cd26d5b37b81bddcc2a9c333a3a7143e2a498a","tid":2193774,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f03c10bd08a5c9599ccc7cf3aec6da86e55fbadc","tid":2193774,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"好似4/3有d都大過full frame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"所以m43等收皮"},{"pid":"836154bfba711378cdfdbd2b85038267bd958b52","tid":2193774,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53bf8cdbb2782f05bc395875580271a734a19391","tid":2193774,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"APSC機仔大撚過Full frame <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:54:46.000Z","msg":"O記一早大左"},{"pid":"957eecfeb30b9510106e8cb5147f4bed927e9b0d","tid":2193774,"uid":296028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:03:21.000Z","msg":"富士問題唔止大仲有貴<br />\nM43很多大光圈定焦都千零二千有交易<br />\n三千內都有等同大三元級的標準變焦"},{"pid":"8ee8ff9c2069549f754eb672e7810b864d018c76","tid":2193774,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"條J有返 18CM 的連登仔<br />\n隻手大通常J都大 <br />\n太細部尾指唔知放邊 <br />\n結論樓主J好短 : 拉"},{"pid":"62fa224e599c18ab3812e65f483d49ffee0b2875","tid":2193774,"uid":296028,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.imaging-resource.com/news/2020/09/04/fujifilm-interview-covid-gfx-strategy-shrinking-ibis-300K-cycle-shutter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imaging-resource.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F09%2F04%2Ffujifilm-interview-covid-gfx-strategy-shrinking-ibis-300K-cycle-shutter&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=0bcb7782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.imaging-resource.com/news/2020/09/04/fujifilm-interview-covid-gfx-strategy-shrinking-ibis-300K-cycle-shutter</a><br />\n<br />\n富士：GFX100 十分成功<br />\n<br />\n1. 影像部門（包括數位相機、instax、光學儀器）整體來說受到疫情衝擊情況可接受。<br />\n  （營收下降12.4%）， 但拒絕提供數位相機部分的營收狀況，看來應該是比較慘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. GFX 100 超乎預期的成功，銷量比預期多 50% 左右。<br />\n   目前以月銷台數來說，GFX 100 是賣得最好的 GF 產品，大概和 50r 數量差不多。<br />\n   50s 的月銷台數大概是 50r 的一半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 富士有意識地跳過所有大廠都在競爭的全幅，認為3000-5000鎂是全幅價格的上限。<br />\n   這個價格帶將是富士主力拓展中幅系統的目標客群。<br />\n   尤其是那些手握全幅單反、並且正在思考是否要轉成全幅無反的用戶，<br />\n   富士希望吸引他們考慮升級中幅。<br />\n<br />\n   目前在 GFX 50r 降價到 3500鎂後，<br />\n   大概 70% 購買 50r 的用戶是從其他廠牌跳來的，反而很少人是從 X 系統升級。<br />\n   證明這個策略有一定成效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 目前 GF 鏡頭銷售的狀況是，每賣出一台機身大概會跟著賣出超過三顆鏡頭。<br />\n   這個數字比 X 系統高非常多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 中幅的優勢在於畫質（不只是畫素數）、中幅成像的 3D 感、<br />\n   動態範圍、高品質鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n6. X-pro 3 向內翻轉的螢幕在設計時收到的使用者回饋就十分兩極，<br />\n   愛的人和討厭的人幾乎各佔一半，而且討厭的人還多一些。<br />\n   但這對小眾產品來說是個好的訊息，表示你有抓到一小群對這個設計買單的人。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}